unittitle_ssm: Mattie E. Hewitt & Richard A. Smith photograph collection
abstract_ssm: The collection contains photographic prints and negatives by noted garden and architecture photographer Mattie Edwards Hewitt and her nephew, Richard Averill Smith. The bulk of the clients are popular magazines and interior decorators. Views of fashionable apartment interiors, newly built houses, small urban gardens, and other residential settings display the work of decorators and the tastes of well-known people. There are also interiors of hotels, restaurants, clubs, shops, and decorator exhibitions.
subject_ssm: Architect-designed houses -- New York (State)  -- New York.
Hotels -- Decoration -- New York (State)  -- New York.
Restaurants -- Decoration -- New York (State)  -- New York.
